title: Authorizes Pets Alive Inc. to file an application for exemption from real property taxes for certain parcels of land located in the town of Wallkill
summary: Authorizes Pets Alive Inc. to file an application for exemption from real property taxes for certain parcels of land located in the town of Wallkill, county of Orange.
actClause: AN ACT to authorize Pets Alive Inc. to file an application for exemption from real property taxes for certain parcels of land located in the town of Wallkill
